arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start()
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_Ulagan_Overlook) then

	id_Ulagan_Clone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(id_Ulagan_Overlook, true)
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_Ulagan_Clone) then

		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(id_Ulagan_Clone, loc_UlaganLeaves_Basin, "NPC_Run", true)
 		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(id_Ulagan_Clone)
		
		end
	
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	-- if sign not previously operated
	if Hydra.IsPlayerVariableSet(idSelf, "QST_Step_SentimentalValue_Sign01Read") == false then
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idSelf, "QST_Step_SentimentalValue_Sign01Read")
		Hydra.EventSend("SentimentalValue_SignRead", idSelf)
		Hydra.IncrementPlayerVariableNumeric(idSelf, "QST_Step_SentimentalValue_SignsRead", 1)
		
		local idUlaganFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Step_Ulagan_Follower")
		
		if Hydra.GetPlayerVariableNumericValue(idSelf, "QST_Step_SentimentalValue_SignsRead") == 1 then
			Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_Ulagan_02b, idSelf, idUlaganFollower)
		else if Hydra.GetPlayerVariableNumericValue(idSelf, "QST_Step_SentimentalValue_SignsRead") == 3 then
			
			Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idSelf, "QST_Step_SentimentalValue_UlaganLoc01")
			Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idUlaganFollower)
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idUlaganFollower, id_Ulagan_Report01, "NPC_RUN", true)
			Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idUlaganFollower, id_Ulagan_Report01)
			Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idUlaganFollower, 0.5)
			-- send user event
			Hydra.EventSend("SentimentalValue_AllSignsRead", idSelf)
			
		end
	end
end
